Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.78,0:00:35.05,From Shiina,,0,0,120,,{\blur10} By the rain-soaked windowsill
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.91,0:00:47.72,From Shiina,,0,0,120,,{\blur10} I hum a nostalgic tune
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.28,0:00:59.72,From Shiina,,0,0,120,,{\blur10} In the emptiness of my young self's heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.94,0:01:12.31,From Shiina,,0,0,120,,{\blur10} A newborn warmth blossoms within
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.88,0:01:27.32,From Shiina,,0,0,120,,{\blur10} Hand in hand, returning home from the seaside dyed red of the sunset
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.33,0:01:32.94,From Shiina,,0,0,120,,{\blur10} What was nothing more than the usual carefree times,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.95,0:01:38.84,From Shiina,,0,0,120,,{\blur10} Had now become very dear moments
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.85,0:01:51.28,From Shiina,,0,0,120,,{\blur10} On the corners of that old photo album, remain traces of teardrops
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.28,0:01:56.85,From Shiina,,0,0,120,,{\blur10} To the one who found them,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.85,0:02:07.28,From Shiina,,0,0,120,,{\blur10} I convey to you, "Thank you, and farewell."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.94,0:02:38.41,To Natsuki,,0,0,120,,{\blur10} As I write this letter,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.91,0:02:50.98,To Natsuki,,0,0,120,,{\blur10} I dream of the good old days
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:03:02.88,To Natsuki,,0,0,120,,{\blur10} Sleeping at the ocean's floor, remaining unnamed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:14.58,To Natsuki,,0,0,120,,{\blur10} A single bud, that will sprout into a pure heart
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:24.28,To Natsuki,,0,0,120,,{\blur10} Hand in hand, we sleep together in the night
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.28,0:03:30.21,To Natsuki,,0,0,120,,{\blur10} Underneath the shining starry sky
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:35.81,To Natsuki,,0,0,120,,{\blur10} That warmth you provided for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.85,0:03:41.88,To Natsuki,,0,0,120,,{\blur10} The feeling lingers in my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:48.31,To Natsuki,,0,0,120,,{\blur10} In these distant, fading memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.31,0:03:54.21,To Natsuki,,0,0,120,,{\blur10} A gentle voice resonates
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:04:02.51,To Natsuki,,0,0,120,,{\blur10} Telling me to pass on to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:08.58,To Natsuki,,0,0,120,,{\blur10} "Thank you, and farewell."
